outputs.output_descr:
Project outputs:
- Strengthened institutional capacities of national malaria control programme/general health services;
- Improved capacities for early diagnosis, adequate treatment, and timely response to malaria outbreaks, including epidemics;
- Support to cost-effective and sustainable vector control;
- Improved capacities for timely response to and prevention of malaria outbreaks and epidemics;
- Reinforced malaria surveillance including in-built mechanisms for monitoring and evaluation and strengthened research capabilities;
- Strengthened research capabilities;
- Increased community awareness and participation in malaria prevention
